content.description: A broken blocky ledge (left of wall) leads to the crux, a horizontal crack through a bulge. Then a nice big hands crack, fist too. And the rest is a romp.
content.location: Look left of the huge roof about 30-40'for blocky ledges leading to crack above. Single bolt before the anchor.

content.description: This route shares the same start as Tea Cup Titties. Instead of going straight up angle to the left using the slanted hand crack. Work your way through this section to the fun hand and fist crack above.
content.protection: Single rack to 3". Rap off the chains at the top and to the left of the route or you can walk off either side.
content.location: This is one of the first routes you will see when you get to the wall from the approach trail.

content.description: This little gem will give you a taste of what the pocket has to offer. It is sunny in the morning and shady after 12.
